title: Lake Merritt in Oakland - Big Spaces - Balcony & Views - Pet Friendly
posting_body: ['Looking for a bigger place with more room to move around, warmth, and amazing natural light?', 'Love the food, activities, and entertainment around Lake Merritt in Oakland?', 'Well, check out 1200 Lakeshore Apartments!', "We're glad to offer this BIG 2Bed, 2Bath hideaway with an East-facing wall of glass.", 'This home is bathed in natural light.', 'Large balcony adds another 340 sqft of covered outdoor space bringing your total indoor-outdoor 1,590 sqft!', 'These building amenities make life more convenient:', '- FREE parking space with each apartment!', '- FREE water, sewer, garbage, and natural gas', '- 24-hour Package Lockers', '- 24-hour Security', '- 24-hour Laundry Facility', '- 24-hour Business Center', '- Mezzanine 4th floor has beautiful outdoor desert garden', '- Gym with dry saunas', '- Luxurious Community Room', '- Available Gigabit Fiber Internet', '- Just moments from Lake Merritt BART', 'Please email or call to schedule your tour today!', 'To see current availability please visit us at <URL>']
